###Context###
#### Functional analysis
+--{: .hide}
[[!include functional analysis - contents]]
=--
=--
=--


A **Dirac distribution** or **Dirac $\delta$-distribution** is a [[distribution]] that is given by evaluating a [[function]] at a point.


